description: [``botocore``] Documentation updates for AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM).
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for AWS Security Token Service.
[``botocore``] adds support for modifying the maintenance window for brokers.

[``botocore``] Amazon CloudFront now provides two new APIs, ListConflictingAliases and AssociateAlias, that help locate and move Alternate Domain Names (CNAMEs) if you encounter the CNAMEAlreadyExists error code.
[``botocore``] Releasing new APIs for AWS Chime MediaCapturePipeline
[``botocore``] This release add storage configuration APIs for AWS IoT SiteWise.
[``botocore``] Adding support for oplocks for SMB file shares,  S3 Access Point and S3 Private Link for all file shares and IP address support for file system associations
[``botocore``] This release adds resource ids and tagging support for VPC security group rules.
